data.description: Welcome to 600 Falling Leaf Way! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom house is now available for sale. Just minutes away from Scott AFB and Mid America Airport, this home offers a range of features and amenities that are sure to impress. As you step inside, you'll notice the inviting atmosphere created by the spacious layout and abundance of natural light. The living area boasts a cozy fireplace, perfect for those chilly evenings. The fenced backyard provides a private oasis where you can relax and unwind. The large owner's bedroom is a true retreat, complete with a walk-in closet that provides ample storage space for all your belongings. Additionally, the upstairs loft area offers versatility and can be used as a playroom, home schooling or additional living space to suit your needs. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your new home. Contact your agent today to schedule a viewing and experience all that 600 Falling Leaf Way has to offer.
